50|$|Statements on Auditing Procedure {{were issued}} by the Committee on Auditing Procedure of the AICPA from 1939 to 1972. The Committee issued 54 SAPs before it became the <b>Auditing</b> <b>Standards</b> Executive Committee (AcSEC) and began issuing Statements on Auditing Standards.Statement on <b>Auditing</b> <b>Standards</b> No. 1 {{summarized}} and superseded the 54 SAPs.|$|R
